---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Google Ads Management Services | OnlineMarketingCORE">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Google Ads Management Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Drive targeted traffic and maximize ROI with our data-driven Google Ads management services.
      </p>
      <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Placeholder for PPC campaign SVG -->
        <div class="bg-gray-200 h-64 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-gray-500">Google Ads Campaign SVG Illustration</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Service Description Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Google Ads Approach</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          At OnlineMarketingCORE, we leverage over 25 years of experience to create high-performing Google Ads campaigns that drive qualified traffic and conversions. Our data-driven approach ensures every dollar of your advertising budget works efficiently to meet your business goals.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We specialize in all aspects of Google Ads, including Search, Display, Shopping, and Video campaigns, tailoring our approach to your specific business needs and target audience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Benefits Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Key Benefits & Outcomes</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Increased Qualified Traffic</h3>
            <p>Attract visitors who are actively searching for your products or services with precisely targeted campaigns.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Improved ROI</h3>
            <p>Our optimization strategies focus on maximizing return on ad spend through continuous testing and refinement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Enhanced Brand Visibility</h3>
            <p>Gain prominent placement in search results and across the Google Display Network to build brand awareness.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Detailed Performance Insights</h3>
            <p>Receive comprehensive reporting with actionable insights into campaign performance and customer behavior.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process Breakdown Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Google Ads Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Account Structure SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Account Structure SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Account Structure</h3>
              <p>We design a strategic account structure that aligns with your business goals, organizing campaigns, ad groups, and keywords for optimal performance and management efficiency.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Keyword Research SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Keyword Research SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Keyword Research</h3>
              <p>Our thorough keyword research identifies high-intent search terms with optimal volume, competition, and relevance to your offerings, incorporating both commercial and informational queries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Ad Creative SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Ad Creative SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Ad Creative Development</h3>
              <p>We craft compelling ad copy and extensions that highlight your unique value propositions, implementing A/B testing to continuously refine messaging and improve click-through rates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Landing Page SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Landing Page SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Landing Page Optimization</h3>
              <p>We analyze and enhance landing pages to ensure they deliver a seamless user experience and compelling conversion points that align with ad messaging, maximizing Quality Score and conversion rates.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="md:w-1/3">
              <!-- Placeholder for Performance Monitoring SVG -->
              <div class="bg-gray-200 h-48 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Performance Monitoring SVG</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-2/3">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Performance Monitoring</h3>
              <p>Our continuous monitoring and optimization process includes bid adjustments, budget allocation refinements, audience targeting improvements, and negative keyword expansion to enhance campaign performance over time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Technology Tools Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Technology Tools We Use</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">We leverage industry-leading tools and proprietary technology to maximize your Google Ads performance:</p>
        <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg">Google Ads Editor</li>
          <li class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg">Google Analytics 4 Integration</li>
          <li class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg">CORE Platform for Advanced Analytics</li>
          <li class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg">Conversion Tracking Solutions</li>
          <li class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg">Automated Bid Management Systems</li>
          <li class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg">Competitive Intelligence Tools</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Pricing & Packages</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Starter</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">For small businesses new to Google Ads</p>
            <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Up to 2 campaigns</li>
              <li>Monthly optimization</li>
              <li>Basic reporting</li>
              <li>Email support</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#contact" class="block text-center py-2 px-4 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-gray-50">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Growth</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">For established businesses seeking expansion</p>
            <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Up to 5 campaigns</li>
              <li>Bi-weekly optimization</li>
              <li>Advanced reporting</li>
              <li>Priority support</li>
              <li>Conversion tracking setup</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#contact" class="block text-center py-2 px-4 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Enterprise</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">For large businesses with complex needs</p>
            <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Unlimited campaigns</li>
              <li>Weekly optimization</li>
              <li>Custom reporting dashboard</li>
              <li>Dedicated account manager</li>
              <li>Full CORE platform integration</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#contact" class="block text-center py-2 px-4 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Case Studies Preview Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Success Stories</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">E-Commerce Revenue Growth</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">A leading online retailer achieved a 135% increase in ROAS (Return on Ad Spend) through our strategic keyword restructuring and enhanced product feed optimization.</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Read Case Study →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">B2B Lead Generation</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Our account restructuring and landing page optimization helped a software company reduce cost-per-lead by 42% while increasing qualified lead volume by 28%.</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 font-medium">Read Case Study →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Expertise Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Google Ads Team</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          Our team consists of certified Google Ads specialists with extensive experience across diverse industries. Each team member undergoes continuous training to stay current with the latest platform updates and advertising strategies.
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="p-4 text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-300 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4"></div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Sarah Johnson</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Google Ads Director</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-300 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4"></div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Michael Chen</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">PPC Specialist</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gray-300 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4"></div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold">Andrea Miller</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Analytics Expert</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Related Services Section -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Related Services</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <a href="../landing-page-optimization" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Landing Page Optimization</h3>
            <p>Improve conversion rates with data-driven landing page enhancements.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="../seo" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">SEO Services</h3>
            <p>Complement your paid search with organic traffic strategies.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="../display-ads" class="block p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Display Advertising</h3>
            <p>Expand your reach with visual ads across the Google Display Network.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How quickly can we expect results from Google Ads?</h3>
            <p>Unlike SEO, Google Ads can drive traffic immediately upon campaign launch. However, optimization for peak performance typically takes 2-4 weeks as we gather data and refine targeting.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">What budget do you recommend for Google Ads?</h3>
            <p>Budget recommendations vary based on industry, competition, and goals. We provide customized recommendations after analyzing your market and objectives, ensuring efficient use of every advertising dollar.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How do you measure the success of our Google Ads campaigns?</h3>
            <p>We establish clear KPIs aligned with your business goals, which may include ROAS, cost per acquisition, conversion rate, or lead quality. Our reporting provides transparent performance metrics and actionable insights.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Can you manage our existing Google Ads account?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we offer comprehensive account audits and seamless transitions for existing accounts. We'll identify opportunities for improvement while preserving historical data and successful campaign elements.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">How often will we receive performance reports?</h3>
            <p>We provide monthly comprehensive reports and ongoing access to our real-time reporting dashboard. For enterprise clients, we offer weekly performance updates and strategy discussions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-blue-700 text-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to transform your Google Ads performance?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8">Schedule a free consultation with our Google Ads experts to discuss your goals and discover how we can help.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="inline-block py-3 px-8 bg-white text-blue-700 font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">Book Your Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout> 
